Please note that the use of `THREAD_ALL_ACCESS` in `OpenThread` may pose a security risk. You should adjust the access rights according to your security policy.

Also, this code assumes that the target process name is "calc.exe". If you want to target a different process, you should replace "calc.exe" with the appropriate name.

Remember to include the necessary headers and define the appropriate constants, such as `NULL` and `THREAD_ALL_ACCESS`, as needed.

